so I draw words and lists.

272
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:35,520
That is fascinating.

273
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:38,520
And by the way, I'm not an artist.

274
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,600
And by the way, I am so glad I asked.

275
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:43,600
People were just sort of, did you just move my name?

276
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:46,600
Might as well have been sketching a cube.

277
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,600
Okay, Roberts and the Annex, everybody think quick.

278
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,600
What do these groups have in common?

279
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,600
Maybe we're supposed to do it with people in our group.

280
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,600
That's not it.

281
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,600
People in the other group?

282
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,600
Hmm, still wrong.

283
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,600
Stanley, you do puzzles all day.

284
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,600
What do we got?

285
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,600
Well, you take the first letter from each name,

286
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,680
assign it a number, add them all up,

287
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,680
and shove it up your butt.

288
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:12,680
Thank you, a little much needed comic relief,

289
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,680
but we really need to figure this out, guys.

290
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,680
It's all a mind game.

291
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,680
He wanted us to see the list.

292
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,680
He's a genius.

293
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,680
You guys just don't get him.

294
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:23,680
I made a list like this for Congress

295
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,680
when I worked in Hollywood in the 50s.

296
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:26,680
They're meaningless.

297
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,680
Guys, really, it's okay.

298
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:30,680
Everyone has made a really solid first impression.

299
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:33,680
I don't think there's any reason for anybody to worry.

300
00:13:33,760 --> 00:13:37,760
I am on the wrong side, and I am freaking out here.

301
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:39,760
I know.

302
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:41,760
It's alphabetical.
